Solful Sessions — Terpene Beverage
Recipe Book
24 Strains × 5 Categories = 120 Terpene-Matched Recipes
Solful Sessions Terpene Pairing Framework v3.0
How This Works
Cannabis and culinary herbs share terpenes—aromatic molecules that create flavor, aroma, and
effects. The Solful Sessions system matches each strain's unique terpene fingerprint to five
distinct beverages across categories: mocktails, cocktails, juices/smoothies, herbal teas, and
wellness shots. Same molecules, different delivery—allowing you to explore terpene pairing
beyond the flower.
The Five Categories
Category Description
Mocktail Sophisticated non-alcoholic drink that mirrors craft cocktail techniques and
complexity.
Cocktail Spirit-forward aperitif or nightcap that deepens the strain's character
through flavor pairing.
Juice /
Smoothie
Blended, nutrient-dense format optimized for terpene absorption and
bioavailability.
Herbal Tea
Blend
Steeped infusion using dried herbs and culinary botanicals to extend the
terpene profile.
Wellness Shot Concentrated, functional format taken as a shot or small sipper for fast
activation.
Energy Tiers
Tier Character Temp/Texture

HIGH Bright, uplifting, energizing Cold, carbonated,
tart
MEDIUM Balanced, social, adaptable Flexible
LOW Grounding, calming, sedating Warm, still, rich
