Wellness Shot: Grounded Truth
A spicy-bright hit of rosemary and lemon clarity.
Glass Shot glass
Volume ~1.5 oz
Temp Room temperature to slightly chilled
Timing Consume immediately after
preparation
Ingredients:
● 1.5 oz Bourbon
● 1 sprig Fresh rosemary (stir)
● 0.25 oz Fresh lemon juice
● pinch Sea salt & rosemary leaf
Method:
1. Infuse 1.5 oz bourbon with a sprig of fresh rosemary for 30 seconds by stirring.
2. Strain out rosemary.
3. Add 0.25 oz fresh lemon juice to the shot glass.
4. Pour bourbon mixture over.
5. Top with a single pinch of sea salt and small rosemary leaf.
