Essential Oil Recipe: Sweet Orange (16 drops), Rosemary (8 drops), Lavender (6 drops),
German Chamomile (6 drops), Black Pepper (4 drops)
Limonene-dominant and uplifting. Sweet orange (40%) captures the orange aroma.
