Cocktail: Cognac Velvet
Cognac's richness deepens nutmeg and cream into sedative bliss.
Glass Snifter
Volume ~4 oz
Temp Warm (140°F)
Style Warm/stirred
Spirit VS Cognac (40% ABV)
ABV ~30%
Ingredients:
● 1.5 oz VS Cognac (warmed)
● 1.5 oz Coconut cream
● 0.25 tsp Freshly grated nutmeg
● 2-3 seeds Fennel seeds (toasted)
Method:

1. Gently warm 1.5 oz VS cognac in a small saucepan (do not boil).
2. Toast 0.25 tsp freshly grated nutmeg and 2-3 fennel seeds together for 15 seconds.
3. Pour warm cognac into snifter.
4. Whisk in 1.5 oz coconut cream carefully.
5. Float spiced mixture on top and garnish with a nutmeg dusting.
