Juice / Smoothie: Pink Rider Juice
Pink grapefruit with lemon cookie sweetness
Volume 8 oz

Temp chilled
Format citrus-apple blend
Timing serve immediately after
preparation
Ingredients:
● 2 fresh pink grapefruits
● 2 fresh lemons
● 2-3 fresh green apples
● 0.5 tbsp lemon curd
● 0.25 oz warm filtered water
● 0.25 oz vanilla extract
● 0.25 oz sugar syrup
● 1.5 oz cold filtered water
● powdered sugar (rim)
● pink grapefruit wheel (garnish)
● lemon peel curl (garnish)
● ice
Method:
1. Juice 2 fresh pink grapefruits through a citrus juicer (yields ~2.75 oz juice).
2. Juice 2 fresh lemons through a citrus juicer (yields ~1 oz juice).
3. Juice 2-3 fresh green apples through a cold press (yields ~0.75 oz juice).
4. Strain all juices through fine mesh.
5. Blend 0.5 tbsp lemon curd with 0.25 oz warm filtered water until smooth.
6. Combine all juices with the lemon curd mixture.
7. Stir in 0.25 oz vanilla extract and 0.25 oz sugar syrup.
8. Add 1.5 oz cold filtered water to reach desired consistency.
9. Pour over ice into a coupe glass rimmed with powdered sugar.
10. Garnish with pink grapefruit wheel and lemon peel curl.
